CentOS 7 安装 CMake 3.17.2
https://www.24kplus.com/linux/557.html

tar -zxf cmake-3.17.2.tar.gz
cd cmake-3.17.2

编译安装
./bootstrap --prefix=/usr --datadir=share/cmake --docdir=doc/cmake && make && make install

检查是否正确安装
cmake --version